15. Telegram From the Department of State to the Embassy in MauritaniaSource: Department of State, Central
                        Foreign Policy File, Electronic Telegrams, D820294–0224. Confidential;
                        Priority. Drafted by Melinda Kimble (AF/W);
                        cleared by Bruce, Bishop, and Bremer; approved by Stoessel. Sent for information to Rabat,
                        Addis Ababa, Nairobi, Paris, Abidjan, Algiers, and Cairo.
